cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this resource, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "NCRA Open Science Ecosystem — research-hub-vi"
abstract: >
  Multilingual open science hub providing interactive access to 45+
  open-access datasets on neuroeconomics, public health, demographics,
  and behavioral economics for Latin America and Ibero-America.
  Includes 33 modules: calculator, timeline, comparator, API explorer,
  semantic search, projections, ethics, methodology, and more.
  Available in 20 languages.
